During an introduction of the show’s game board Friday, grinning  host Alex Trebek reportedly unveiled a series of highly intrusive categories about current champion James Holzhauer’s personal life before snickering, “Let’s see you answer these, James.”“You’ve been able to handle pretty much everything else we’ve thrown at you, but these clues might just wipe that fucking smirk off your face,” Trebek said as the studio lights abruptly darkened in tandem with a booming, ominous sound cue, introducing the game’s Double Jeopardy categories, which included “Times James Pissed His Pants,” “Reasons James’ Father Is Disappointed In Him,” and “How James’ Wife Really Feels About Him.” “Go ahead, smart-ass.